title: Gotham a.k.a. The Dead Can't Lie
description:
Tommy Lee Jones
Virginia Madsen

Jones plays a private detective who gets paid by a millionaire to tell his dead wife to leave him alone who is stalking him for 10 years.

And then it all starts. Is she a ghost ? Is this all a scamm ? Who&#039;s crazy and what&#039;s real ?
